             <h3 class="title">
              <a href="/news/remembering-the-deadly-oso-landslide-7-years-later">
               Remembering the deadly Oso landslide 7 years later
              </a>
             </h3>
            </header>
            <p>
             Monday, March 22 marks the seven-year anniversary of the deadly Oso landslide, which killed 43 people in 2014.
            </p>
            <time class="time" datetime="2021-03-21T16:14:55-07:00">
             4 hours ago
            </time>
            <!-- -->
           </div>
          </article>

               <img alt="Minute of Mayhem: Watch armed marijuana robbers quickly terrorize clerks and customers; help ID suspects" data-src="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2021/03/592/333/bell-main.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" data-srcset="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2021/03/1184/666/bell-main.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1 2x" data-v-0cd7fcba="" src="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2021/03/32/18/bell-main.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0);width:592px;margin:auto;height:0;padding-top:56.25%;"/>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/phase-3-of-washingtons-pandemic-recovery-plan-could-help-revive-live-entertainment-silenced-by-covid-19">
                Phase 3 of Washington's pandemic recovery plan could help revive live entertainment silenced by COVID-19
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              StartingMonday, March 22, the entire state moves to Phase 3 of Washingtons Roadmap to Pandemic Recovery. Phase three means indoor businesses like restaurants, shops, gyms and movie theaterscan welcome back customers at up to 50 percent capacity.
             </p>
             <!-- -->
             <!-- -->
            </div>
           </article>
           <article class="article post story-2" data-v-711e7e86="">
            <!-- -->
            <div class="m">
             <a href="/news/all-counties-in-washington-advancing-to-phase-3">
              <div class="responsive-image__container" data-v-0cd7fcba="">
               <div class="responsive-image__lazy-container" data-v-0cd7fcba="" style="background-image:url('https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2021/01/592/333/C5221F3983B74835ADC542F2AB257FD6-e1609893336725.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1');">
                <img alt="All counties in Washington advancing to Phase 3 on Monday" data-src="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2021/01/592/333/C5221F3983B74835ADC542F2AB257FD6-e1609893336725.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" data-srcset="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2021/01/1184/666/C5221F3983B74835ADC542F2AB257FD6-e1609893336725.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1 2x" data-v-0cd7fcba="" src="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2021/01/32/18/C5221F3983B74835ADC542F2AB257FD6-e1609893336725.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0);width:592px;margin:auto;height:0;padding-top:56.25%;"/>
               </div>
               <noscript data-v-0cd7fcba="">
                <picture class="responsive-image__picture" data-v-0cd7fcba="">

            <div class="m">
             <a href="/news/seattle-public-school-superintendent-to-resign-before-contract-expires">
              <div class="responsive-image__container" data-v-0cd7fcba="">
               <div class="responsive-image__lazy-container" data-v-0cd7fcba="" style="background-image:url('https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2020/06/592/333/juneau1.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1');">
                <img alt="Seattle public school superintendent to resign before contract expires" data-src="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2020/06/592/333/juneau1.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" data-srcset="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2020/06/1184/666/juneau1.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1 2x" data-v-0cd7fcba="" src="https://images.foxtv.com/static.q13fox.com/www.q13fox.com/content/uploads/2020/06/32/18/juneau1.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0);width:592px;margin:auto;height:0;padding-top:56.25%;"/>

               <noscript data-v-0cd7fcba="">

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/the-divide-with-brandi-kruse/brandi-kruse-congress-knows-how-to-fix-border-crisis">
                Brandi Kruse: Congress knows how to fix border crisis
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              Each week on"The Divide":Brandi Kruse offers a commentary that looks for common ground on issues that divide us. Topics include gun control, free speech, policing, and politics.
             </p>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/trump-adviser-says-former-president-is-starting-his-own-social-media-platform-after-permanent-ban-from-others">
                Trump adviser says former president is starting his own social media platform after permanent ban from others
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              After being banned from social media for inciting violence ahead of the Jan. 6 riot, a senior adviser to former president Donald Trump says Trump has plans to make a comeback online by creating his own social media platform.
             </p>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/house-passes-equality-act-which-would-enshrine-lgbtq-protections-in-us-labor-and-civil-rights-laws">
                House passes Equality Act, which would enshrine LGBTQ protections in US labor and civil rights laws
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              The Democratic-led House passed a bill Thursday that would enshrine LGBTQ protections in the nation's labor and civil rights laws, a top priority of President Joe Biden, though the legislation faces an uphill battle in the Senate.
             </p>

             <!-- -->

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/money/home-warranty-vs-homeowners-insurance-difference">
                What's the difference between home warranty and homeowners insurance?
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              A home warranty and homeowners insurance may both cover your home, but each offers distinct protection. Learn more about what you need as a homeowner.
             </p>
